==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skittle
<hw>Skit"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to the
game of skittles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Skittle alley</b></col>, <cd>an alley or court in which
the game of skittles is played.</cd> -- <col><b>Skittle ball</b></col>,
<cd>a disk or flattish ball of wood for throwing at the pins in the game
of skittles.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Skittle-dog</ent>⟦br⟧
